{
  "answer": "> **Matla (opening couplet) of Ghazal 204 from *Diwan-e-Ghalib***:\n\n**Original (Urdu):**  \nیہ نہ تھی ہماری قسمت کہ وصال_یار ہوتا  \nاگر اور جیتے رہتے یہی انتظار ہوتا[^1]\n\n**Transliteration:**  \nYeh na thi hamari qismat ke visaal-e-yaar hota  \nAgar aur jeete rehte yahi intezaar hota[^2]\n\n**Translation:**  \nTo be with my Beloved was not my fate;  \nHad I lived longer, waiting was my state.[^3]\n\n[^1]: Mirza Ghalib, *Diwan-E-Ghalib*, [p-0ed9be](/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/204-yeh-na-thi-hamari-qismat-ke-visaal-e-yaar-hota/original/#p-0ed9be).\n\n[^2]: Mirza Ghalib, *Diwan-E-Ghalib*, [p-007848](/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/204-yeh-na-thi-hamari-qismat-ke-visaal-e-yaar-hota/transliteration/#p-007848).\n\n[^3]: Mirza Ghalib, *Diwan-E-Ghalib*, [p-e43078](/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/204-yeh-na-thi-hamari-qismat-ke-visaal-e-yaar-hota/translation/#p-e43078).",
